data.description: Welcome to luxury living in Vistancia! This Maracay home is a masterpiece of modern design and comfort, boasting 4 bedrooms and 3 baths. Benefit from cost-efficient living with solar panels. Step into the heart of the home - the kitchen. A chef's dream, it showcases nearly Bosch stainless steel appliances, a gas range, farmhouse sink, and stunning quartz countertops. Illuminate your culinary adventures with under-counter lighting and discover convenience in the large walk-in pantry featuring a stylish sliding barn door. The well-thought-out floorplan includes a downstairs bedroom and full bath, offering flexibility. Ascend to the upper level to find the master suite, where luxury meets functionality. Enjoy your private balcony retreat & bask in the Arizona sunsets.The primary bedroom's... en suite is a spa-like oasis, tastefully updated with a double sink vanity, a glass-enclosed shower, a separate soaking tub, and custom tile. A generously sized walk-in closet completes this haven of relaxation. Step outside to an entertainer's paradise in the backyard. An extended covered patio beckons gatherings, overlooking a lush grassy area. Discover tranquility by the fruit trees or at the koi pond - a perfect setting for outdoor enjoyment. This home seamlessly blends style, comfort, and eco-friendliness. Don't miss the chance to make this Maracay masterpiece your own! Enjoy all of the outstanding Vistancia amenities, including a community pool, playground, tennis court and much more!
